title: David Gilmour - Live In Gdansk Special Edition
description:
David Gilmour - Live In Gdansk

It's a 5 disc version, I didn't include disc 3, because it's the dvd of what's on the audio cd's 1 and 2.

All files in mp3-format, vbr.
Cover image present.


Disc 1 - Concert
1.Speak to Me
2.Breathe
3.Time
4.Breathe (Reprise)
5.Castellorizon
6.On an Island
7.The Blue
8.Red Sky at Night
9.This Heaven
10.Then I Close My Eyes
11.Smile
12.Take a Breath
13.A Pocketful of Stones
14.Where We Start

Disc 2 - Concert
1.Shine On You Crazy Diamond
2.Astronomy Domine
3.Fat Old Sun
4.High Hopes
5.Echoes
6.Wish You Were Here
7.A Great Day for Freedom
8.Comfortably Numb


Disc 4
Three track from the Mermaid Theatre performance in 2006
1.Shine on You Crazy Diamond
2.Wearing the Inside Out
3.Comfortably Numb

Two tracks from the AOL Sessions, 2006
4.On an Island
5.High Hopes

Three track from Live From Abbey Road
6.The Blue
7.Take a Breath
8.Echoes (Acoustic)

Three track from the never-before heard jams from The Barn, January 2007
9.Barn Jam 166
10.Barn Jam 192
11.Barn Jam 121

1.Shine On You Crazy Diamond - Venice, 12 August 2006 & Vienne, 31 July 2006

3.The Blue - Vienne, 31 July 2006

6.Coming Back to Life - Florence, 2 August 2006
7.Find the Cost of Freedom - Manchester, 26 May 2006
8.This Heaven - Vienne, 31 July 2006
9.Wearing the Inside Out - Milan, 25 March 2006
10.A Pocketful of Stones - Vienne, 31 July 2006
11.Where We Start - Vienne, 31 July 2006
12.On the Turning Away - Venice, 12 August 2006
